        @George: try using a different web browser, one that you haven't used before for microblog on this computer. If that gives you the correct theme then the other browser has the files from the old theme in its cache. Unfortunately many browser assume static files never change. While this does not directly apply to your case, see the following stack overflow question for some ideas on how to force browsers to reload files: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/126772/how-to-force-a-web-browser-not-to-cache-images
       </p>
      </div>
